room_title: Escape room "Brainwashed" by UFO VIDEO in Gainesville
room_address: 605 NW 53rd Ave Suite A8a Gainesville, FL 32609
room_description:
Based on VHS tapes reportedly stolen from a 1980's CIA mind-control testing laboratory, Brainwashed exposes players to a series of mysterious audiovisual transmissions that aid them in defeating the alien Polybius Virus.
This 60-minute game is appropriate for all ages, but not recommended for players with medical conditions related to light sensitivity.
